high_descs: Turn right and walk to the door, then turn right and face the table next to the door.
Pick up the knife that is left of the bread on the table.
Slice half the loaf of bread; the loaf closer to you.
Still holding the knife, turn right and walk through the kitchen to the wall, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the knife on top of the fork on the counter.
Turn left, walk to the door, then turn right and face the table next to the door.
Pick up one slice of bread, the second one from the left (not an end-piece).
Holding the slice of bread, turn right and walk to the beginning of the kitchen.  Turn right to face the microwave on the counter.

Open the microwave door, put the slice of bread inside the microwave, and close the microwave door.  Microwave the bread for a few seconds, then take out the slice of bread and shut the microwave door.
Holding the slice of bread, turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen.  Turn left to face the counter to the right of the stove top.
Put the slice of bread on the counter behind the knife to the right of the black cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved slice of bread on the counter by the stove top.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the white table on your right.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Slice the loaf of bread closest to you in several pieces.
Turn right, head towards the window, and then turn left to face the counter.
Place the knife behind the fork on the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the white table on your right.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn around and head towards the microwave.
Place the bread in the microwave, heat it up, and take it back out.
Turn left, walk towards the window, and then turn left to face the counter.
Place the bread to the right of the cup nearest to you.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife along with a slice of bread on the counter to the right of the stove.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk towards the table. Turn right and face the table.
Pick up the silver knife on the table.
Slice the bread on the table.
Pick up the knife and turn to the right. Walk straight forward then turn to the left.
Place the knife on the counter top below the fork.
Turn to the left walk back to the table and turn right.
Pick up the second slice to the left.
Turn around completely and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the bread inside. Warm up the bread in the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward then turn left to go across to the other counter top.
Put the bread on the counter top below the spatula and to the right of the mug.
anns.task_desc: Slice bread warm it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn and go to the table where the stool is.
Pick up the knife on the table.
With the knife slice half the loaf of bread that is closest to you.
Turn and with the knife in hand go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the knife on the counter directly behind the fork that is there.
Go back to the table to the bread that is sliced.
Pick up the second piece from the left of sliced bread.
With the slice of bread in hand go to the microwave.
Open the microwave door and put the slice of bread in the center of the microwave and shut the door.  Start the microwave.  When finished open the door and get the slice of bread.  Close the door.
With the slice of bread in hand go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the slice of bread behind the knife and to the right of the coffee mug on to the counter.
